{"tid":833833,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"當年嘅07四子","createTime":"2018-09-23T19:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T04:05:37.000Z","uid":73827,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd8b104cbe5d36735448ca61448045349248ff2","tid":833833,"uid":73827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T19:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/030048_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F030048_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=4be0e986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳柏宇 周柏豪 洪卓立 小肥<br />\n<br />\n而家望番轉頭，當年其實有4個平分秋色嘅新人真係幾正，cd鋪會播佢地嘅歌，頒獎禮會關心邊個攞獎，4間公司，各有hit歌，各有特色，雖然後尾立立走正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小肥又衰個樣，但起碼叫有精彩過，而家都唔太差。<br />\n<br />\n望番而家，坤哥，削骨，後庭，全部都一陣tvb味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會有人關心佢地出歌，攞獎，真係有啲唏噓<br />\n<br />\n甚至覺得07年已經算係香港樂壇最後一批有代表性嘅年代，因為我唔相信10年後仲會有人聽坤哥嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n90後廣東歌迷深夜有感而發，有冇90後巴打有一樣feel"},{"pid":"6c1df3d2f0ed58b9f48ed7851c09103eb4f7081a","tid":833833,"uid":203456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:12:45.000Z","msg":"而家聽番陳栢宇啲舊歌仲好有feel"},{"pid":"1b010a0ee7779aa64b69724706a86f4a7e550b7d","tid":833833,"uid":140252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T20:35:33.000Z","msg":"小肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樂壇遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733d2532629acfa5838faf8038fd4bfe8ae75076","tid":833833,"uid":56870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"完全有feel<br />\n果年新人 起碼聽得入耳 <br />\n同埋圑結過打後出道新人"},{"pid":"113a31fac3165860aa26c69513b1e85b36b8c680","tid":833833,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"其實覺得小肥唱得幾好， 但咁多年最有印象都係得首寵物。"},{"pid":"77c6b74925a9a00d58247bf722aad9d05d0e2dde","tid":833833,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"立立英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a4ce8d46b87f7adbed967cd5c8616a326e52b6","tid":833833,"uid":73827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"113a31fac3165860aa26c69513b1e85b36b8c680","tid":833833,"uid":39706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"其實覺得小肥唱得幾好， 但咁多年最有印象都係得首寵物。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"唱功佢真係屌打，最正應該係時光機同負親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3206a138576eab5a4fa94818313aa660be0a279","tid":833833,"uid":73827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733d2532629acfa5838faf8038fd4bfe8ae75076","tid":833833,"uid":56870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"完全有feel<br />\n果年新人 起碼聽得入耳 <br />\n同埋圑結過打後出道新人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"佢地啲歌真係唔差，上年都見到佢地食飯，仲有hotcha嗰啲"},{"pid":"052ec6ed666fb8293891365cde85f032bede962f","tid":833833,"uid":73827,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77c6b74925a9a00d58247bf722aad9d05d0e2dde","tid":833833,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"立立英年早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"立立近幾年啲歌其實幾正"},{"pid":"6ad0fa6cb0652257b428bd42e438b70bb1d2300b","tid":833833,"uid":39706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{